Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.73,Style_text_Mami,,0,0,0,,Ну как, страшно?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.98,Style_text_Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Вот ещё!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.90,Style_text_Madoka,,0,0,0,,Я боюсь...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.04,Style_text_Madoka,,0,0,0,,Но...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:14.24,Style_signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz13\c&HA8B7DA&\bord1.5\move(657,97.5,847.5,102,0,4049)}Гертруда
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.06,0:19:14.21,Style_text_Kyuubey,,0,0,0,,Быстрее! Мы почти в центре поля!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:20.25,Style_signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(967.5,717)\bord0\c&H000000&\fnTimes New Roman\fs37.5}Гертруда
